Process called "build_rsa_pkcs1v15_sha256_oid" takes arena as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: 1.2.840.113549.1.1.11 -> DER body 2A 86 48 86 F7 0D 01 01 0B.
    Let buf be Arena.arena_allocate(arena, 9)
